snippet.title: Toripon 鳥ポン - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Take photos of cute birds doing cute things, and make people happy on the internet.

Toripon 鳥ポン lets you explore the fantasy of affording a nice apartment, having far too many pet birds and spending your days documenting their cuteness for the world to see. Coming soon!

Available exclusively on itch.io - https://theladyvictoria.itch.io/toripon
